      "citation_id": "[CITATION_5]",
      "span_text": "Tang et al. reported that the leaching efficiency of Xiangxi manganese oxide ore reached 99.8% under the optimal conditions: mass ratio of manganese ore to waste tea 10:1, 1.7 mol/L sulfuric acid, a liquid/solid ratio of 7.5:1, and a leaching temperature of 368 K for 8 h."
